Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:10.61,bt,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(140,0)}第4话 「无法停止的{\1c&2338ab&}超{\1c&HFFFFFF&}振动」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优米尔大人 这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你即将穿在身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超振动装备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问 超振动装备是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依靠超振动水晶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展开特殊的力场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将敌人的攻击全部弹开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究极的铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.00,0:02:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要 要 要我当斗士什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是为了你家人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.09,0:02:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这身铠甲的特点是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手的攻击越强 水晶的振动也会越强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而产生强大的力场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那老实站着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.76,0:03:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是伟大的炼金术师·希昂的魔导石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.31,0:03:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而能承受住这份力量的这副身体也真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有点太敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.17,0:04:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集钢铁山所有的知识和技术于一身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大陆最强斗士计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于 其第一号实验体完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超振动战乙女·美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.90,0:04:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,号外 号外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,满版都是大事件的报道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在各地被目击到的谜之光的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否从月亮降临的最强斗士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡里巴拉的深处 浓雾的密林中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探险队捕获了传说中的珍兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.23,0:04:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 竟竟竟竟竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王大人的私生子疑云
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷鸣之夜出生的三胞胎姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欲知详情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请君解囊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老百姓就是喜欢看那种大事件 温迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以把这些提供给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.07,0:05:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也说不上是真实的报道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 要早点到盖纳斯去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.41,0:05:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到美莉姆才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.90,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预言中出现的「命运之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的通缉犯 乖乖就范吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就差「偶然」发生的「命运的再会」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体里长出了奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我采访下么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:58.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.65,0:06:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是通缉犯的同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为为为什么会变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究极的铠甲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有配套的武器哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预测敌人的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自动攻击敌人的究极武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超振动剑·无限利刃以及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（Infinite Slasher）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超振动盾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请鉴赏我之计划的成果吧 女王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:07:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这玩意在实战中可没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾丽娜 你要来试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了姐姐大人一剑还能毫发无伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我已经站不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤依特 已经安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥竟然是女人 真让我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要再叫我哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会改的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.01,0:08:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为事到如今再改称呼又不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想死你了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 还以为再也见不到哥哥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我离开克莱因城堡的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明想向你好好道别的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没能见到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为现在和你重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤依特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要去找姐姐大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我当斗士什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那身铠甲只有我才能脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优米尔大人 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不干的话 钱就泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优米尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事 慌慌张张的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.79,0:10:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从返回的侦察队中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了在索罗尔附近 目击到安妮洛特的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到这么快就有实战测试的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那个机器人及其主人也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤依特？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要赶快做好出击的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不出我的五指山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我的确需要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为此要跟尤依特战斗的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是美斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿着这铠甲 身体不能随心所欲地活动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道到底该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝将拯救所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说出你的烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你逃到哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都可以根据铠甲上水晶发出的波动追踪到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:12:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这难道是 恶魔附体？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是因此而祈求上帝的庇护吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违抗上帝的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝啊 请用您的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用神之光照耀她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救赎她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做的话 会变得更激烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔在抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的恶魔 从她身上滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都无法驱逐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就将你视为异端 施以火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来在这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是神圣的教会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有中央教王厅的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为所欲为的话我会很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是异端审问官·斯琪大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那能请你高抬贵手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她还给我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美莉姆 给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去击败反抗女王的安妮洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安妮洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在此分别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.60,0:15:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥又要去别的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去女王的首都·盖纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去盖纳斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去找被钢铁参谋·优米尔带走的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.32,0:15:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还必须夺回被偷走的妈妈的魔导石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:16:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再见吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事的家伙走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.18,0:16:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回终于可以跟姐姐来个「命运的再会」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:04.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是赢了你 弟弟们就可以填饱肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了弟弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点投降的话 不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我越使劲她力气就更大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是找到美莉姆 就和她一起吃顿美味大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天赚了不少 预算足够了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候没机会交给哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着总有一天要给她 一直带在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山茶花的花语是「强大与骄傲」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和哥哥真衬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续的话 我就要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于该命运的邂逅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.21,0:19:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温迪 要救哥哥了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭飞拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就来 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:19:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤依特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么美莉姆会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那名斗士到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是我正在找的朋友 美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤依特的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的美莉姆不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她既关心家人又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人一定是知道了她生活拮据 才强迫她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷了魔导石的 也一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股不可思议的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许与希昂大人的魔导石有关联
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是为了这个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢铁参谋·优米尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.04,0:21:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去盖纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:57.07,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,正義の剣は折れ 無機質に転がった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:22:02.44,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,支えてた自分 reasonとか 見えなくなってしまうの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:07.61,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,左手で掴んでも 右手からこぼれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:12.70,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,泣いてなんかいないのに 霞んで行く情景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:17.99,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆらり揺れて 惑わす世界はきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:22.45,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,未来切符を探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:28.50,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,鈍い音に 焦らされるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:32.68,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,走り出さなきゃ ゴールはない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:39.00,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,future is serious! future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:44.41,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,なんで、どうして、心が邪魔をするの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.57,0:22:46.78,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:56.19,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,何十回繰り返しても 戸惑いを振り払って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.46,0:23:06.27,edjap,NTP,0,0,0,,立ち上がる まだ夢を見たまま…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢铁参谋·优米尔大人竟然对我的身体做那种实验
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.86,0:23:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我早说了我当不了斗士了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安妮洛特姐姐大人不快点投降的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.40,0:23:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就再也忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为了妈妈她们 必须要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.89,0:23:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一话 盖纳斯城的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 那里绑成那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道龙战士是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.86,0:23:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级受虐狂吗
